overview.longBusinessSummary: Yum China Holdings, Inc. owns, operates, and franchises restaurants in the People's Republic of China. It operates through two segment: KFC and Pizza Hut. The company also provides online food deliver services. It operates restaurants under the KFC, Pizza Hut, Taco Bell, Lavazza, Little Sheep, and Huang Ji Huang brands. Yum China Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
